transaction_index.column_description: Integer of the transactions index position log was created from

address.column_description: Address from which this log originated

block_number.column_description: The block number where this log was in

data.column_description: Contains one or more 32 Bytes non-indexed arguments of the log

topics.column_description: Indexed log arguments (0 to 4 32-byte hex strings). (In solidity: The first topic is the hash of the signature of the event (e.g. Deposit(address,bytes32,uint256)), except you declared the event with the anonymous specifier.)

transaction_hash.column_description: Hash of the transactions this log was created from

log_index.column_description: Integer of the log index position in the block

block_timestamp.column_description: Timestamp of the block where this log was in

block_hash.column_description: Hash of the block where this log was in
